sec.p:
For European options, the spot price of the underlying bond must be adjusted for the payment of discrete dividends by the stocks in the S&P 500 basket. As in Bakshi, Cao, and Chen (1997) and Dumas et al. (1998), we assume these cash flows to be perfectly anticipated by market participants. For each contract traded on daytwith days to expiration DTE, we first calculate the present value
